{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "root-001",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Deep Learning Basics\nUnit 1 Overview",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 100,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "branch-ml-vs-dl",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### Traditional ML vs. Deep Learning\nManual vs. Automated Feature Extraction",
      "x": -450,
      "y": -200,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "leaf-feature-eng",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Feature Engineering**\nIn ML, human experts must manually extract features (edges, color histograms) before feeding them to classifiers.",
      "x": -850,
      "y": -320,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "leaf-auto-learning",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**End-to-End Learning**\nIn DL, raw data is fed directly. The hidden layers learn hierarchical features automatically.",
      "x": -850,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "branch-dl-drivers",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### What Drives Deep Learning?\nWhy it became popular recently",
      "x": 450,
      "y": -200,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "leaf-big-data",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Big Data Era**\nNeural networks scale with more data. Standard ML performance plateaus; DL keeps improving.",
      "x": 850,
      "y": -320,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "leaf-gpu-compute",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**GPU Acceleration**\nMassive parallel calculations (matrix multiplies) are handled efficiently by graphics cards.",
      "x": 850,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "branch-apps",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### Key Applications\nWhere DL is used today",
      "x": -450,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "leaf-computer-vision",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Computer Vision**\nSelf-driving cars, facial recognition, medical imaging (tumor scans).",
      "x": -850,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "leaf-nlp",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Natural Language Processing**\nVoice assistants (Siri, Alexa), Google Translate, Large Language Models (ChatGPT).",
      "x": -850,
      "y": 260,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "branch-challenges",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### Major Challenges\nLimitations and blockers",
      "x": 450,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "leaf-black-box",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Black Box Problem**\nLack of explainability. Difficult to understand *why* the network made a certain decision.",
      "x": 850,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "leaf-data-compute-cost",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Resource Cost**\nRequires millions of labeled training instances and high electricity/hardware costs.",
      "x": 850,
      "y": 260,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "1"
    }
  ],
